Libusb needs to be installed to "/system/lib" before pyusb will work. 

See: https://github.com/libusb/libusb/tree/master/android

* Build libusb for android and then install to android system:

    adb push obj/local/armeabi/libusb1.0.so /sdcard/
    adb shell
    su
    mount -o remount,rw /system
    cat > /system/lib/libusb1.0.so < /sdcard/libusb1.0.so
    chmod 644 /system/lib/libusb1.0.so
    cat > /system/bin/listdevs < /sdcard/listdevs
    chmod 0755 /system/bin/listdevs
    mount -o remount,ro /system



